> Getting Started with Nomadnet
Welcome to the mesh network! This guide will help you get started.  
>> What is Nomadnet?
Nomadnet is a `!decentralized communication system`! built on top of `[Reticulum`https://reticulum.network]. It enables:  
  • Secure messaging
  • Off-grid communication
  • `*Privacy-focused`* networking
  • Community mesh networks
-
>> Installation
Follow these steps to get started:  
  Install Python 3.7 or higher
  Run `=pip install nomadnetwork`=
  Launch with `=nomadnet`=
  Create your first page!
